{"word":"ὅλμος","slug":"ὅλμος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ὅλμος</b></el> <el>(ὅλμος, ὁ,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:εἴλω'><el>εἴλω</el></a>, <i>volvo</i>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a round smooth stone, a roller</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>any round body: a mortar</i>, <b><a href='S:Hesiod'>Hes.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>: <i>a kneading-trough</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}